# metadataObjects

**Instance Property**

The list of metadata objects captured at this synchronization timestamp.

## Declaration

```swift
var metadataObjects: [AVMetadataObject] { get }
```

## Discussion



This array is equivalent to that provided by the [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCaptureMetadataOutputObjectsDelegate/metadataOutput(_:didOutput:from:)] delegate method when using a metadata capture output without a data output synchronizer.
